<br>
IMO though there are only three really good choices after Run3: Regen3 (always helps when you're hurt), Meta3 (especially if you use stat food), or advanced bandaging if you plan on staying around level 60 and soloing outside of PoP a lot (warrior soloing isn't really an option in PoP).<br>
